smart on crime seizing on opportunities in times of crisis events at stanford smart on crime seizing on opportunities in times of crisis facebook twitter email print add to calendar california attorney general kamala d harris will present smart on crime seizing on opportunities in times of crisis she will speak about her innovative efforts to reduce recidivism and promote public safety students will also get an opportunity to ask her about her career trajectory and her priorities for the ca department of justice the event is presented by the stanford center for criminal justice and professor joan petersilla when thursday october 27 2011 11 00 am approximate duration of 1.5 hour s where stanford law school room 290 map audience faculty staff alumni friends general public students tags lecture reading sponsor stanford law school contact programs law stanford edu admission please register at http www stanford edu dept law forms kamala fb permalink http events stanford edu events 295 29525 last modified october 26 2011
